sentences: Sünkopeeritud rütmiga ragtime tekkis USA-s viljeldud rahvaliku muusika liik.
Afroameerika rütmielementide kandudes Euroopa muusikavormidesse tekkis uus muusikastiil.
context: The word 'tekkis' is the past tense of the verb 'tulla', which means 'to come' or 'to arise'. In this context, it indicates that something came into existence or appeared. The dictionary definition shows its usage in describing how ragtime music emerged when African American rhythmic elements were incorporated into European musical forms.
